5, 165.5203, 164.4604, 164.342, 163.8412, 164.4192, 162.5624, 164.3263, 164.6967, 165.6148, 168.1196, 170.1463, 167.484, 167.9183, 167.1387, 169.6979, 171.3719, 170.8738, 174.7965, 174.4135, 174.1858, 175.9744, 177.2707, 177.6262, 173.6578, 173.7952, 174.9207, 175.2573, 175.4682, 177.0507, 177.6953, 179.3092, 177.5611, 179.184, 181.6571, 180.8378, 180.1221, 183.0788, 186.8719, 188.4191, 187.9316, 189.4797, 193.5553, 197.3477, 194.2644, 195.266, 197.9779, 195.7141, 197.6298, 196.8086, 198.273, 196.0658, 194.7623, 194.1056, 194.851, 196.9716, 197.0048, 197.6513, 198.6783, 199.605, 201.0251, 200.337, 201.4543, 201.9589, 202.5568, 202.493, 202.6702, 202.7006, 203.5163, 203.1351, 202.7665, 203.3006, 202.1638, 202.0272, 201.8787, 202.5061, 202.4845, 202.6773, 203.3043, 202.8987, 202.6256, 202.3889, 200.6726, 200.8251, 201.0166, 202.179, 201.428, 201.0367, 202.3369, 202.8059, 203.2268, 203.3531, 204.1421, 203.8306, 200.2163, 201.4797, 200.2856, 199.6758, 198.8998, 197.3361, 197.3525, 197.5976, 196.852, 197.0864, 197.509, 197.9765, 196.8751, 197.6478, 197.804, 198.857, 198.6017, 199.4868, 198.9323, 198.9563, 198.068, 197.3733, 198.745, 199.0765, 198.2673, 198.3521, 199.2842, 200.0264], "summary_html": "<h1>20200101_paper_Beta_Risk_in_the_Cross-Section_of_Equities</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p><strong>信号构造（严格按 <code>strategy_final.py</code>，变体 <code>acx_dual_h21_raw</code>）</strong>：</p>\n<p>1. <strong>日频简单收益</strong>：<code>ret = close.pct_change()</code>（按 sym 分组，向后差分，无前视）。 2. <strong>等权商品市场收益</strong>：每个交易日对全部品种的 <code>ret</code> 取均值得 <code>mkt_ret</code>，merge 回面板。 3. <strong>按市场方差分解（vardiff）</strong>：方差代理 <code>mkt_var_proxy = mkt_ret²</code>；其 <strong>rolling-252 中位数</strong>（min_periods=120）为阈值。高方差日（proxy ≥ 中位数）保留 <code>ret_hv/mkt_hv</code>，低方差日保留 <code>ret_lv/mkt_lv</code>；分别做 rolling-252（min=60）OLS beta 得 <code>beta_hv</code>、<code>beta_lv</code>；<code>beta_vardiff = beta_hv − beta_lv</code>。 4. <strong>按市场收益分解（retdiff）</strong>：阈值用 <code>mkt_ret</code> 的 <strong>rolling-252 均值</strong>（min=120）。高收益日保留 <code>ret_hr/mkt_hr</code>，低收益日保留 <code>ret_lr/mkt_lr</code>；分别 rolling-252（min=60）OLS beta 得 <code>beta_hr</code>、<code>beta_lr</code>；<code>beta_retdiff = beta_hr − beta_lr</code>。 5. <strong>双重截面 rank 组合</strong>：在两者均非空的样本上做横截面分位 <code>cr_rank</code>：<code>_rr = rank(beta_retdiff)</code>、<code>_rv = rank(beta_vardiff)</code>。组合 <code>_rk_avg = [(1 − _rr) + _rv] / 2</code>，即 <strong>做多低 retdiff（1−rank）+ 做多高 vardiff（+rank）</strong>。 6. <strong>连续方向</strong>：<code>_sig = (_rk_avg − 0.5) × 2</code>，映射到 [−1, 1] 的连续方向 <code>direction</code>。 7. <strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：<code>vol_target_scale</code>（target=0.15 年化，vol_window=60，max_leverage=3.0），position = direction × 0.15 / (日对数收益 rolling-60 std × √252)，clip 到 ±3。 8. <strong>月度调仓</strong>：<code>rebalance_hold(hold_days=21)</code>，每 21 个交易日重置一次信号、之间前向填充。</p>\n<p><strong>方向逻辑</strong>：retdiff 取「做多低值」（<code>1 − rank</code>），vardiff 取「做多高值」（<code>+rank</code>）——低 retdiff = 在市场高收益日相对 beta 不高（无追涨暴露），高 vardiff = 在市场高方差日 beta 反而更高的属性被赋多头；二者等权合成。</p>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>：实盘化 corr vs Polars 基线 = 1.0；样本内（2016–2025）Sharpe ≈ 0.9，样本外（2025+）Sharpe = 1.67，meta Sharpe = 1.03；retdiff/vardiff 双信号正交，组合后非冗余入库。<strong>防前视</strong>：所有 rolling 均为 trailing 窗口，<code>pct_change</code> 向后差分，阈值 rolling 中位数/均值与 beta 估计窗口均只用历史数据，<code>rebalance_hold</code> 仅前向填充，执行由下游 T+1 open 处理。</p>\n<blockquote>⚠️ Polars 保真细节：<code>mkt_var_med</code> / <code>mkt_ret_ma252</code> 两个阈值列在参考 strategy.py 中是 <strong>全局 rolling（无 <code>.over('sym')</code>）</strong>，在 [sym, datetime] 排序的面板上每个品种前 ~252 行会掺入前一品种尾部数据。<code>strategy_final.py</code> 刻意复刻此行为以与基线对齐（per-sym 分组只能到 corr 0.8976，全局 rolling 才到 1.0），并非前视，仅是 warm-up 期的基线保真。</blockquote>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.87</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-13.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.02</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3434</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.67</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.18 / 0.73</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.39</span></td><td>0.59</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.56</span></td><td>1.33</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td><td>1.14</td><td>1.2</td><td>0.05</td><td>1.23</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.37</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.08</span></td><td>0.31</td><td>1.98</td><td>1.38</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.04</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3436</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>94.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>记品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span>、日期 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span>，收盘价 <span class=\"math-tex\">P_{i,t}</span>。</p>\n<p><strong>日收益与市场收益</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r_{i,t} = \\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-1}} - 1, \\qquad r^{m}_t = \\frac{1}{N_t}\\sum_{i} r_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>滚动 OLS beta（窗口 <span class=\"math-tex\">W=252</span>，min 60）</strong>：对任意配对 <span class=\"math-tex\">(y, x)</span>，</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\beta = \\frac{\\operatorname{Cov}_W(y,x)}{\\operatorname{Var}_W(x)} = \\frac{\\mathrm{E}_W[yx] - \\mathrm{E}_W[y]\\,\\mathrm{E}_W[x]}{\\sigma_{W}(x)^2}, \\qquad \\beta = 0 \\ \\text{if}\\ \\sigma_W(x) \\le 10^{-10}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mathrm{E}_W[\\cdot]</span>、<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_W</span> 为 rolling-<span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> 均值/标准差。</p>\n<p><strong>方差分解（split 窗口 252，min 120）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">v_t = (r^m_t)^2, \\quad \\tilde v_t = \\operatorname{median}_{252}(v),\\quad\n<p>\\beta^{hv}_{i} = \\beta(r_{i}, r^m \\mid v \\ge \\tilde v),\\ \\ \\beta^{lv}_{i} = \\beta(r_{i}, r^m \\mid v &lt; \\tilde v)</div></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vardiff}_{i,t} = \\beta^{hv}_{i,t} - \\beta^{lv}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>收益分解（split 窗口 252，min 120）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\bar r^m_t = \\operatorname{mean}_{252}(r^m),\\quad\n<p>\\beta^{hr}_{i} = \\beta(r_{i}, r^m \\mid r^m \\ge \\bar r^m),\\ \\ \\beta^{lr}_{i} = \\beta(r_{i}, r^m \\mid r^m &lt; \\bar r^m)</div></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{retdiff}_{i,t} = \\beta^{hr}_{i,t} - \\beta^{lr}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>横截面双重 rank 信号</strong>（<span class=\"math-tex\">\\operatorname{rank}_t</span> 为当日 percentile rank <span class=\"math-tex\">\\in[0,1]</span>）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\rho^{rr}_{i,t} = \\operatorname{rank}_t(\\text{retdiff}),\\quad \\rho^{rv}_{i,t} = \\operatorname{rank}_t(\\text{vardiff})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">s_{i,t} = \\frac{(1 - \\rho^{rr}_{i,t}) + \\rho^{rv}_{i,t}}{2},\\qquad d_{i,t} = (s_{i,t} - 0.5)\\cdot 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标仓位</strong>（vol_window=60，min 20）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\ell_{i,t} = \\ln\\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-1}},\\quad \\sigma^{ann}_{i,t} = \\sigma_{60}(\\ell_{i})\\cdot\\sqrt{252}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w^{raw}_{i,t} = \\operatorname{clip}\\!\\left(d_{i,t}\\cdot \\frac{0.15}{\\sigma^{ann}_{i,t}},\\ -3,\\ 3\\right)\\quad(\\sigma^{ann} &gt; 10^{-8},\\ \\text{否则}\\ 0)</div>\n<p><strong>月度调仓</strong>（hold <span class=\"math-tex\">H=21</span>，按品种内序号 <span class=\"math-tex\">k</span>，1-based）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{i,t} = \\begin{cases} w^{raw}_{i,t}, &amp; (k_{i,t}-1)\\bmod H = 0 \\\\ w_{i,t-1}, &amp; \\text{否则（前向填充）}\\end{cases}</div>\n<p>最终输出列 <code>position</code> = <span class=\"math-tex\">w_{i,t}</span>。变体后缀 <code>_raw</code> 表示返回原始信号，<code>_cs/_ts</code> 归一化、重采样到日频与 gross 缩放由 build pipeline 的 <code>postprocess_positions</code> 统一处理。</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>BETA_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>rolling beta lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>BETA_MIN</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>min periods for beta</td></tr><tr><td><code>SPLIT_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>rolling window for high/low var &amp; ret threshold</td></tr><tr><td><code>SPLIT_MIN</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>min periods for threshold</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>monthly rebalance</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 2.14s</li>\n</ul>"}